rom  to  in that role he led the global financial services and media businesses which provide information analytics and technology services to professionals in the financial services media and corporate markets globally as well as to individuals through its consumer media arm from  to  mr wenig was chief operating officer of reuters a provider of financial market data in that role he led reuters consumer media and internet strategy and was responsible for the companys data information and analytical products as well as the sales information technology and global marketing functions prior to that mr wenig served on the reuters board of directors and was president of reuters business divisions from  to  where he was responsible for leading the revitalization of reuters and its four business segments mr wenig currently is a member of the business council he also serves as the cochair of the world economic forums consumer industries steering committee and as a trustee of the paley center for media mr wenig received his ba from union college and his jd from columbia university school of law source ebay inc on  ¬† sign up for equilar atlas and view devin n wenigs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like devin n wenig more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in devin n wenigs network and community follow changes in devin n wenigs employment and moneyinmotion connect with devin n wenig through your network of conections view full profile ¬† search for over  executive profiles bio example devin n wenig devin n wenigs connections  sign up now to view devin n wenigs  connections ¬ª scott d cook board member the procter  gamble company steven c quay chairman of the board president and chief executive officer atossa genetics inc michael r jacobson former senior vice president legal affairs general counsel and secretary ebay inc scott thompson board member coupa software i